<!-- AI TOOL -->
<div class="box">
<h2>ðŸ¤– AI Hashtag Generator (Smart & Trending)</h2>
<p class="note">Uses AI â€“ caption based, niche & trending hashtags</p>

<textarea id="aiInput" placeholder="Enter caption or topic..."></textarea>
<button onclick="aiHashtags()">Generate AI Hashtags</button>
